{"type": "article", "id": 23455, "title": "蓝色盒子的茶叶包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-08T07:30:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 79, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702170805HQfTsUyZAdE2okbz.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这组茶叶包装使用了非常亮丽的蓝色，长方体的盒子后面用文件袋一样的扣子连接，体现出古典和精致。封面上以白底黑字的形式标注信息，有银色的花体字，增加了光泽感，也让人联想起精装书。Noble &amp; Savage 是一个初创的品牌，他们强调茶叶的健康和优良品质。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021708025OGJMEWSmayudxQI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021708033CjuU1xa7SLpH2MG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170804Qp5Cawdqkn6HWu7X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170804RSVDXzptTFjxwGsC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021708059ufZ2F0jzGiNM1XO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}